description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, which features a text fight, Mary waiting for FedEx, and more! After the recap, Danny chats with Alexia Echevarria, formerly of The Real Housewives of Miami, about a potential reboot, what she's been up to since the show stopped filming, and more!


Alexia Interview: 28:23ish


PS Subscribe to Danny's spinoff podcast, A Very Merry Iconic Podcast, which is out now!
